    "We collect results for baselines from public reports (Xiong et al., 2024).",
    "Method PubmedQA MedMCQA Mixtral 8*7B (2024) 67.6 56.4 Llama2 70B (2023b) 50.4 43.1 Meditron 70B (2023) 56.4 52.7 PMC-llama 13B (2024) 42.6 65.2 ChatQA-1.5 8B (2024b) 66.4 46.9 ChatQA-1.5 70B (2024b) 74.8 62.5 RankRAG 8B (2024) 65.0 56.9 RankRAG 70B (2024) 79.8 69.1 GPT-3.5 (2022) 67.4 66.7 GPT-4-0613 (2024) 70.6 66.7 MA-RAG (Llama3-8B) 66.7 56.5 MA-RAG (Llama3-70B) 78.9 67.9 MA-RAG (GPT-4o-mini) 80.2 69.8",
    "Other Domains We further assess the generalizability of our method by conducting experiments in other domains.",
